13_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Findian-banks-rush-for-clients-set-for-reckoning-after-paytm-fiasco-124022100313_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Findian-banks-rush-for-clients-set-for-reckoning-after-paytm-fiasco-124022100313_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Maratha%20Quota-A%20Short-Term%20Measure%20For%20Electoral%20Gains%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fieo2sndo_manoj-jarange_625x300_26_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20legislative%20assembly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-bill-passed-in-maharashtra-assembly-5092654%5C%22%3Epassed%20a%20bill%20(Maharashtra%20State%20Socially%20and%20Educationally%20Backward%20Bill%202024)%20providing%2010%25%20reservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fmarathas-get-10-quota-as-bill-passed-in-maharashtra-assembly-763094%5C%22%3EMaratha%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20education%20and%20government%20jobs.%20The%20state%20government%20had%20convened%20a%20one-day%20special%20session%20of%20the%20legislature%20for%20the%20same.%20The%20decision%20was%20taken%20following%20a%20comprehensive%20report%20submitted%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Backward%20Class%20Commission.%20The%20survey%20for%20the%20same%20had%20included%20nearly%202%20crore%20people%2C%20and%20it%20aimed%20to%20find%20out%20the%20nature%20and%20extent%20of%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20educational%20backwardness%20faced%20by%20the%20Maratha%20community%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20the%20Maratha%20community%20comprises%2028%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%20The%20community%2C%20otherwise%20politically%20powerful%2C%20has%2021.22%25%20of%20its%20families%20living%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%2C%20exceeding%20the%20state's%20average%20of%2017.4%25.%20The%20survey%20also%20highlighted%20that%2094%25%20of%20farmer%20suicides%20in%20Maharashtra%20involve%20Maratha%20families.%20This%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-quota-bill-draft-similar-to-bill-struck-down-by-court-sharad-pawar-5094987%5C%22%3Ethird%20time%20in%20a%20decade%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20state%20introduced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-quota-maratha-reservation-eknath-shinde-brings-maratha-quota-bill-despite-history-of-court-setbacks-5091647%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Attempts%252C%2520The%2520Setbacks%2Cnow%2520be%2520tabled%2520in%2520Assembly.%5C%22%3Elegislation%20for%20Maratha%20quota.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2017%2C%20the%20'Mahayuti'%20government%20%5Ban%20alliance%20comprising%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%5D%20had%20assured%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%2C%20who%20had%20been%20on%20a%20hunger%20strike%2C%20that%20a%20special%20session%20of%20the%20assembly%20would%20be%20called%20on%20February%2020%20to%20complete%20the%20procedures%20for%20granting%20reservation%20to%20the%20community.%20However%2C%20Jarange%20himself%20has%20rebuffed%20the%20latest%20bill%2C%20calling%20it%20'vote-bank%20politics'%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetrayal%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20reservation%20granted%20is%20not%20under%20the%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20category.%20Jarange%2C%20who%20has%20been%20demanding%20that%20Kunbi%20certificates%20be%20issued%20to%20all%20Marathas%2C%20accused%20Maharashtra%20minister%20and%20NCP%20leader%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%20of%20jeopardising%20the%20issue.%20The%20Kunbi%20community%20falls%20under%20the%20OBC%20category%20and%20Bhujbal%2C%20an%20OBC%20leader%2C%20has%20been%20opposing%20the%20reservation%20for%20Marathas%20under%20the%20category.%20Allowing%20the%20Maratha%20community%20into%20the%20OBC%20fold%20would%20mean%20parting%20with%20some%20share%20of%20the%20quota.%20Sources%20even%20say%20that%20the%20BJP%20used%20Bhujbal%20to%20stonewall%20the%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EA%20Possible%20Legal%20Challenge%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fmaratha-quota-bill-passed-will-it-stand-legal-scrutiny-763062%5C%22%3Ethe%20bill%20will%20stand%20legal%20scrutiny%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20also%20a%20subject%20of%20concern%2C%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20previous%20attempts%20were%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20court's%20cap%20of%2050%25%20reservations%20would%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20Shinde%20government-Maharashtra%20reservations%20are%20already%20at%2052%25%2C%20and%20the%20latest%20Maratha%20quota%20will%20push%20it%20further.%20In%20earlier%20cases%2C%20the%20court%20had%20rejected%20state%20surveys%20that%20stated%20the%20Maratha%20community%20was%20socially%2C%20economically%20and%20educationally%20backward.%20How%20the%20government%20plans%20to%20convince%20the%20court%20this%20time%20will%20be%20eagerly%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20feel%20that%20the%20current%20dynamics%20within%20the%20ruling%20coalition%2C%20where%20each%20party%20seeks%20to%20be%20the%20dominant%20player%2C%20has%20forced%20the%20Shinde%20government%20to%20take%20this%20step%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20elections.%20%26quot%3BThe%20opposition%20in%20Maharashtra%20claims%20that%20this%20is%20just%20a%20gimmick%20by%20the%20government%20ahead%20of%20elections.%20They%20also%20feel%20it%20will%20be%20challenged%20in%20courts%2C%20which%20will%20strike%20down%20the%20proposal%20as%20the%20Marathas%20do%20not%20fit%20into%20the%20economically%20or%20socially%20backward%20category%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Rohit%20Chandavarkar%2C%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20political%20analyst.%20%26quot%3BGetting%20Marathas%20votes%20may%20benefit%20the%20government%20in%20the%20elections%2C%20and%20%5Bit%20knows%5D%20very%20well%20that%20the%20courts%20will%20knock%20it%20down%20later.%26quot%3B%20Both%20Shinde%20and%20NCP's%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20another%20Maratha%20leader%2C%20realise%20that%20the%20three-party%20bonhomie%20may%20not%20last%20long%20given%20the%20BJP's%20aspirations%20to%20win%20maximum%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20BJP's%20Maratha%20Outreach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leadership%20has%20long%20sought%20to%20bring%20Maratha%20leaders%2C%20who%20have%20traditionally%20been%20Congress-NCP%20voters%2C%20on%20its%20side%20and%20enhance%20its%20vote%20base%2C%20along%20with%20the%20support%20of%20urban%20voters%2C%20OBCs%20and%20upper%20castes.%20The%20crossing%20over%20of%20influential%20Maratha%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20into%20the%20BJP%20has%20given%20impetus%20to%20the%20party's%20plan%20of%20consolidating%20its%20vote%20base%20in%20the%20community.%20Chavan%2C%20son%20of%20the%20late%20S.B.%20Chavan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20early%20Maratha%20leaders%2C%20enjoys%20mass%20support%20in%20parts%20of%20Marathwada%20region%20and%20among%20Marathas%20in%20general%20across%20the%20state.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20another%20Maratha%20leader%2C%20Narayan%20Rane%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20with%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20was%20welcomed%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%202019%20and%20made%20a%20union%20minister.%20The%20party%20knew%20that%20Rane%20could%20influence%20the%20state's%20Maratha%20votes%20and%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20take%20on%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20the%20Konkan%20region.%20However%2C%20Rane%20has%20been%20keeping%20a%20low%20profile%20since%20the%20political%20winds%20shifted%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20BJP%20allied%20with%20Shinde-also%20a%20Maratha%20ladder-to%20form%20the%20government%20in%20June%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20also%20inducted%20other%20Congress%20leaders%20such%20as%20Harshvardhan%20Patil%20and%20Radhakrishna%20Vikhe%20Patil%20to%20challenge%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20hold%20over%20sugarcane%20farmers%20in%20Western%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EImage%20Makeover%20For%20Shinde%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ongoing%20Maratha%20quota%20agitation%2C%20Shinde%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20commanding%20leader%2C%20a%20neutraliser%20trying%20to%20diffuse%20the%20situation%20created%20by%20Jarange's%20stir%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20not%20part%20of%20the%20negotiations.%20Sources%20say%20Shinde%20was%20not%20happy%20about%20Ajit%20Pawar%20joining%20the%20alliance%20government%20and%20feels%20the%20move%20was%20meant%20to%20challenge%20his%20stature%20and%20create%20a%20competing%20Maratha%20faction%20within%20the%20government.%20There%20also%20have%20been%20instances%20of%20open%20tussles%20between%20the%20two.%20Now%2C%20Jarange's%20agitation%20has%20given%20Shinde%20an%20opportunity%20to%20settle%20the%20score%20and%20create%20a%20'mass%20leader'%20image%20for%20himself.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20seems%20it's%20for%20the%20first%20time%20Shinde%20is%20leading%20on%20his%20own%2C%20without%20the%20apparent%20support%20of%20his%20strong%20deputies%20Fadnavis%20and%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20seems%20to%20have%20completed%20its%20groundwork%20and%20social%20engineering%20in%20Maharashtra%20for%20the%20coming%20elections.%20The%20Modi%20factor%20and%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%20might%20add%20to%20its%20vote%20share%20too.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20also%20undercurrents%20of%20resentment%20among%20middle-class%20Maharashtrians%20over%20the%20BJP's%20politics%20of%20splitting%20parties%20to%20form%20a%20coalition%20government.%20Many%20feel%20that%20such%20politics%20has%20impacted%20developmental%20work%20in%20the%20state.%20If%20this%20perception%20continues%2C%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%2C%20due%20in%20late%202024%2C%20might%20throw%20up%20an%20unfavourable%20result%20for%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708497420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fieo2sndo_manoj-jarange_625x300_26_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaratha-quota-a-short-term-measure-for-electoral-gains-5098553%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Experts%20feel%20the%20current%20dynamics%20within%20the%20ruling%20coalition%2C%20where%20each%20party%20seeks%20to%20be%20the%20dominant%20player%2C%20has%20forced%20the%20Shinde%20government%20to%20take%20this%20step%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaratha-quota-a-short-term-measure-for-electoral-gains-5098553%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaratha-quota-a-short-term-measure-for-electoral-gains-5098553%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaratha-quota-a-short-term-measure-for-electoral-gains-5098553%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20United%20flight%20was%20diverted%20after%20passengers%20spotted%20that%20parts%20of%20the%20plane%20wing%20were%20chipped%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225425%5C%22%2