king%20about%20capability%2C%20do%20we%20need%20to%20remind%20that%20had%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEbBC5VSmFn%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEbBC5VSmFn%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1iskZ0QGbr%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1iskZ0QGbr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20BJP%20West%20Bengal%20(%40BJP4Bengal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBJP4Bengal%2Fstatus%2F1759972964060020777%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2020%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20face-off%20took%20place%20when%20Mr%20Adhikari%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20which%20has%20hit%20headlines%20amid%20allegations%20of%20land%20grab%20and%20extortion%20against%20local%20Trinamool%20leaders.%20The%20BJP%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20aides%20of%20Trinamool%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20had%20sexually%20harassed%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Bengal%20BJP%20said%20state%20police%20officers%20had%20reduced%20themselves%20to%20%26quot%3Bdoormats%26quot%3B%20of%20Trinamool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%2C%20BJP%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bhad%20no%20business%20getting%20hot%20under%20the%20collar%2C%20when%20it%20was%20him%20who%20was%20violating%20Calcutta%20High%20Court's%20order%2C%20by%20restricting%20LoP's%20movement%3F%20Under%20what%20provision%20did%20he%20stop%20the%20delegation%20when%20the%20single%20bench%20judge%20had%20approved%20LoP's%20visit%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhamakhali%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20witnessed%20high%20drama%20yesterday%20when%20Bengal%20police%20stopped%20Mr%20Adhikari%20from%20proceeding%20to%20the%20island%20despite%20a%20court%20order%20allowing%20him.%20He%20was%20eventually%20allowed%20to%20visit%20after%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court's%20nudge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPS%20officer%2C%20BJP%20said%2C%20was%20acting%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20agent%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20was%20hoping%20that%20the%20division%20bench%20would%20stay%20the%20single%20bench%20order%26quot%3B.%20The%20officer%2C%20it%20alleged%2C%20kept%20holding%20up%20the%20BJP%20delegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concerned%20officer%20is%20in%20contempt%20of%20Court.%20It%20is%20a%20shame%20that%20the%20WB%20Police%20is%20willing%20to%20be%20a%20political%20pawn%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20is%20dragging%20in%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20said.%20It%20stressed%20that%20none%20of%20its%20leaders%20used%20the%20derogatory%20term%2C%20and%20accused%20the%20officer%20of%20using%20the%20occasion%20%26quot%3Bto%20attract%20undue%20attention%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20questioned%20why%20Bengal%20police%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20arrest%20Shahjahan%20yet.%20The%20strongman%20has%20been%20missing%20since%20a%20mob%20of%20his%20supporters%20attacked%20a%20team%20of%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20that%20had%20gone%20to%20Sandeshkhali%20for%20a%20raid%20against%20him%20in%20a%20corruption%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSheikh%20Shahjahan%20is%20absconding%20for%2050%20days%20now.%20WB%20Police%20should%20also%20wear%20it%20as%20a%20medal%20and%20reflect%20on%20their%20non-existent%20'capability'.%20Go%2C%20arrest%20him%2C%20if%20you%20are%20'capable'%20enough.%20Just%20today%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20has%20issued%20instruction%20to%20arrest%20Shahjahan%20and%20added%20that%20the%20state%20should%20not%20protect%20him.%20Does%20this%20shame%20WB%20Police%3F%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20BJP%20also%20shared%20visuals%20of%20Bengal%20police%20taking%20Sikh%20protesters%20into%20custody%20with%20their%20turbans%20off.%20%26quot%3BHere%20is%20a%20video%20and%20images%20to%20remind%20how%20disrespectful%20WB%20Police%20has%20been%20towards%20the%20Sikhs.%20You%20have%20pulled%20off%20tur