k%20At%20Milestones%20In%20Fali%20Nariman's%20Career%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFali%20S%20Nariman%2C%20distinguished%20jurist%20and%20senior%20advocate%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20died%20today.%20He%20was%2095.%20The%20senior%20lawyer%20had%20been%20suffering%20from%20multiple%20ailments%2C%20including%20cardiac%20issues.%20In%20a%20career%20that%20spanned%20seven%20decades%2C%20Mr%20Nariman%20was%20part%20of%20several%20key%20legal%20matters%2C%20many%20of%20them%20related%20to%20crucial%20Constitutional%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20facts%20about%20Fali%20S%20Nariman%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBorn%20in%20Rangoon%20in%201929%2C%20he%20completed%20schooling%20from%20the%20prestigious%20Bishop%20Cotton%20School%20in%20Shimla%20and%20then%20completed%20a%20Bachelor's%20in%20Arts%20from%20Mumbai's%20St%20Xavier's%20College.%20He%20got%20his%20law%20degree%20from%20Government%20Law%20College%2C%20also%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20Bar%20and%20Bench%2C%20Mr%20Nariman%20had%20said%20%26quot%3Blaw%20was%20the%20last%20option%20for%20me%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BMy%20father%20wanted%20me%20to%20take%20the%20Indian%20Civil%20Service%20exam%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20he%20couldn't%20afford%20it.%20I%20had%20secured%20a%20second%20class%20in%20my%20B.A.%20degree%20and%20there%20was%20no%20other%20choice%20other%20than%20law%2C%20as%20I%20had%20no%20sense%20of%20science%20or%20mathematics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20started%20his%20legal%20career%20in%201950%20as%20an%20advocate%2C%20practising%20in%20Bombay%20High%20Court.%20His%20exceptional%20expertise%20earned%20him%20the%20designation%20of%20senior%20advocate%20in%201961.%20He%20moved%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20a%20Senior%20Advocate%20in%201971%2C%20a%20position%20he%20retained%20till%20the%20end.%20He%20served%20as%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20from%201972%20to%201975%2C%20when%20he%20stepped%20down%20to%20protest%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20then%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20crucial%20case%20he%20was%20part%20of%20was%20the%20legal%20battle%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%201984%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Tragedy%20that%20killed%20at%20least%203%2C800%20people%20and%20affected%20lakhs.%20Mr%20Nariman%20appeared%20for%20Union%20Carbide%2C%20which%20ran%20the%20facility.%20Much%20later%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20on%20CNN-IBN%2C%20he%20regretted%20that%20decision.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20one%20is%20always%20ambitious%20at%20that%20age.%20But%20I%20found%20later%2C%20but%20then%20it's%20too%20late.%20One%20can't%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20case%20one%20has%20already%20taken%20up...%20it%20was%20not%20a%20case%3B%20it%20was%20a%20tragedy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnother%20key%20case%20he%20was%20part%20of%20was%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20Constitutional%20amendment%20to%20set%20about%20a%20National%20Judicial%20Appointments%20Commission%20to%20replace%20the%20Collegium%20system%20for%20appointing%20judges.%20Arguing%20against%20the%20new%20system%2C%20the%20jurist%20had%20said%20the%20proposed%20commission%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20anathema%20to%20judicial%20independence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20his%20contributions%20to%20jurisprudence%2C%20he%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%20and%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20and%20several%20international%20awards%2C%20including%20the%20Gruber%20Prize%20for%20Justice.%20He%20was%20a%20nominated%20member%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20between%201999%20and%202005%20and%20served%20on%20multiple%20legal%20panels.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nariman%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20son%20Rohinton%20Fali%20Nariman%2C%20a%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20daughter%20Anaheeta%20and%20daughter-in-law%20Sanaya.%20His%20wife%20Bapsi%20Nariman%20died%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708496760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ftn97g2og_fali-nariman_625x300_21_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremembering-fali-s-nariman-renowned-senior-advocate-and-legal-icon-who-died-at-95-5098106%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fali%20S%20Nariman%2C%20distinguished%20jurist%20and%20senior%20advocate%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20died%20today.%20He%20was%2095.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremembering-fali-s-nariman-renowned-senior-advocate-and-legal-icon-who-died-at-95-5098106%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremembering-fali-s-nariman-renowned-senior-advocate-and-legal-icon-who-died-at-95-5098106%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremembering-fali-s-nariman-renowned-senior-advocate-and-legal-icon-who-died-at-95-5098106%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China-born%20Australian%20democracy%20blogger%20decides%20against%20appealing%20suspended%20Chinese%20death%20sentence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708496681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107873761%2Cimgsize-965088.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fchina-born-australian-democracy-blogger-decides-against-appealing-suspended-chinese-death-sentence%2Farticleshow%2F107873662.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107873662.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fchina-born-australian-democracy-blogger-decides-against-appealing-suspended-chinese-death-s