e%20victory%2C%20the%20Congress%20described%20it%20as%20the%20prevailing%20mood%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20electorate%20ahead%20of%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Puttana%20polled%208%2C260%20votes%2C%20JD%20(S)%20candidate%20Ranganath%20had%206%2C753%20votes.%20Puttanna%20secured%20the%20victory%20by%20a%20margin%20of%201%2C507%20votes.%20Out%20of%20the%20total%2016%2C063%20votes%20cast%2C%201%2C000%20votes%20were%20rejected%20on%20account%20of%20them%20being%20%E2%80%98invalid%E2%80%99.%20The%20by-poll%20to%20the%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20constituency%20seat%20in%20the%20Council%20involves%20voting%20by%20registered%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20for%20Puttanna%2C%20this%20is%20the%20fifth%20straight%20win%20from%20the%20constituency%2C%20and%20he%20recorded%20victories%20from%20all%20three%20parties%2C%20now%20with%20Congress%2C%20and%20earlier%20with%20BJP%20and%20JD%20(S).%20The%20by-poll%20was%20necessitated%20after%20he%20quit%20the%20seat%20in%20March%202023%20to%20contest%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20but%20lost%20the%20poll.%20Before%20joining%20the%20BJP%20in%202020%2C%20Puttanna%20had%20won%20the%20Council%20poll%20thrice%20on%20JD%20(S)%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Congress%20chief%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20D.K.%20Shivkumar%20said%20the%20by-poll%20result%20is%20an%20indicator%20of%20things%2C%20especially%20given%20that%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20around%20the%20corner.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20say%20that%20some%20BJP-JD(S)%20leaders%20claimed%20that%20the%20polls%20will%20be%20an%20indicator%20of%20things%20to%20come.%20The%20results%20have%20come%20and%20Puttanna%20of%20the%20Congress%20has%20won%20the%20polls.%20He%20has%20won%20for%20the%20fifth%20consecutive%20time.%20The%20voters%20who%20are%20educated%20and%20are%20teachers%20have%20rejected%20the%20BJP-JD(S)%20(alliance)%20and%20have%20voted%20for%20the%20Congress.%20The%20same%20mood%20will%20prevail%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shivakumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fkarnataka-powerplay-congress-records-first-win-against-bjp-jds-alliance-in-legislative-council-bypoll-9172085%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20also%20weighed%20in.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20constituency%20is%20the%20one%20which%20Puttanna%20had%20resigned%20from%20to%20contest%20the%20Assembly%20elections.%20He%20is%20contesting%20for%20the%20fifth%20time.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20he%20has%20defeated%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20JD(S).%20He%20has%20the%20support%20of%20the%20teachers%20and%20has%20also%20won%20their%20hearts%20and%20this%20has%20helped%20him%20win%20the%20teachers%E2%80%99%20constituency%20four%20times%20in%20a%20row.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victory%20of%20Puttana%2C%20however%2C%20will%20not%20change%20the%20scenario%20in%20the%2075-member%20legislative%20council%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20and%20JD%20(S)%20combine%20has%20the%20upper%20hand.%20The%20BJP%20has%2034%20members%2C%20the%20Congress%2029%2C%20the%20JD(S)%208%2C%20and%201%20Independent%20member%2C%20besides%20the%20chairman%20and%20two%20vacancies%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708495837000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21111156%2FUntitled-design-10-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findicator-of-political-mood-in-karnataka-says-congress-as-party-wins-legislative-council-seat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20victory%20of%20Puttanna%20assumes%20significance%20given%20that%20it%20is%20the%20first%20electoral%20test%20following%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20BJP-JD(S)%20alliance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22