%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2020)%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20Bill%20reserving%2010%25%20seats%20in%20educational%20institutions%20and%20government%20jobs%20for%20the%20Maratha%20community.%20This%20is%20the%20third%20time%20a%20Bill%20of%20this%20kind%20has%20been%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20the%20first%20two%20attempts%20were%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20courts%20as%20being%20legally%20unsound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20states%20that%20those%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98creamy%20layer%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20excluded%20from%20this%20reservation.%20All%20three%20Bills%20have%20been%20introduced%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20elections.%20This%20time%20too%2C%20Maratha%20community%20leaders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpune%2Fmaratha-groups-express-apprehension-over-quota-bill-allege-it-is-a-poll-trick%2Farticleshow%2F107868763.cms%5C%22%3Ehave%20argued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Bill%20is%20an%20electoral%20trick%20and%20will%20not%20stand%20the%20legal%20test%20in%20courts%20as%20it%20has%20not%20been%20properly%20formulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20introduced%20the%20Bill%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20Maratha%20community%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20and%20educational%20backwardness%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20it%20says%20was%20established%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Backward%20Class%20Commission%20survey.%20However%2C%20this%20claim%20is%20rife%20with%20controversy%20as%20six%20members%20of%20the%20Commission%20%E2%80%93%20including%20its%20chairman%2C%20Justice%20(retired)%20Anand%20Nirgude%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmaratha-quota-panel-3-more-members-chairman-quit-citing-government-interference%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20state%20government%20was%20interfering%20with%20its%20work%20and%20trying%20to%20force%20them%20into%20declaring%20the%20Maratha%20community%20as%20backward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20Maratha%20leaders%20who%20have%20been%20agitating%20for%20the%20reservation%20are%20unconvinced%20by%20the%20new%20Bill.%20Manoj%20Jarange%2C%20who%20had%20become%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Maratha%20protests%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Maratha%20community%20should%20have%20been%20included%20in%20the%20OBC%20community%20instead%20of%20being%20added%20as%20a%20separate%20reserved%20section.%20%E2%80%9CGovernment%20has%20given%20us%20a%20separate%20reservation%20which%20crosses%2050%25%20ceiling%20and%20which%20does%20not%20stand%20the%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fall-parties-pass-10-maratha-quota-bill%2Farticleshow%2F107866687.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20disappointed%20with%20govt%20and%20especially%20with%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20who%20had%20taken%20a%20pledge%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20that%20he%20would%20be%20giving%20reservation%2C%20but%20today%E2%80%99s%20decision%20will%20not%20stand%20legal%20scrutiny%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pravin%20Indulkar%2C%20advocate%20and%20Maratha%20activist%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpune%2Fmaratha-groups-express-apprehension-over-quota-bill-allege-it-is-a-poll-trick%2Farticleshow%2F107868763.cms%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%20that%20the%20new%20Bill%20closely%20resembled%20the%20two%20others%20that%20had%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20courts.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20draft%20of%20the%20bill%20cleared%20by%20state%20legislature%20today%20is%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20the%20one%20presented%20before%20the%20apex%20court.%20We%20need%20to%20see%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20fresh%20bill%20in%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%