%20capital%20Islamabad%20close%20to%20midnight%20local%20time%20on%20Tuesday.%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20will%20be%20prime%20minister%20while%20Bhutto%20Zardari's%20father%2C%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%2C%20will%20be%20nominated%20as%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20the%20parties%20have%20the%20numbers%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%2035%2C%20the%20son%20of%20slain%20former%20premier%20Benazir%20Bhutto%2C%20said%2C%20with%20his%20father%20and%20Sharif%20next%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20will%20probably%20end%20days%20of%20uncertainty%20after%20the%20inconclusive%20February%208%20election%2C%20in%20which%20Khan's%20candidates%2C%20running%20as%20independents%2C%20defied%20the%20odds%20by%20winning%20the%20most%20seats%20but%20fell%20short%20of%20clinching%20an%20outright%20majority.%20Rounds%20of%20negotiations%20followed%2C%20culminating%20in%20the%20announcement%20Tuesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestors%20will%20be%20watching%20what%20this%20means%20for%20Pakistan's%20markets%2C%20which%20have%20been%20rocked%20after%20the%20polls.%20The%20benchmark%20stock%20index%20has%20fallen%20for%20six%20of%20eight%20trading%20days%20since%20February%208.%20Dollar%20bonds%20due%202031%20climbed%201.2%20cents%20to%2066.04%20cents%20on%20the%20dollar%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20while%20notes%20maturing%202051%20also%20rose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20also%20remain%20about%20how%20Khan's%20supporters%20will%20respond.%20His%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party%20posted%20on%20X%20a%20picture%20of%20Sharif%2C%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20and%20his%20father%20moments%20after%20the%20announcement%2C%20using%20the%20hashtag%20%23MandateThieves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%2C%20also%20known%20as%20PTI%2C%20held%20protests%20over%20the%20weekend%20against%20alleged%20vote-rigging.%20Its%20claims%20were%20bolstered%20when%20a%20Pakistani%20official%20said%20he%20had%20manipulated%20the%20vote%20count%20-%20and%20that%20th