ed%20a%20coalition%20after%20Khan%20was%20ousted%20in%20April%202022%20and%20ruled%20the%20country%20for%20about%2016%20months.%20Shehbaz%20was%20prime%20minister%2C%20while%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20was%20his%20foreign%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20period%2C%20Bhutto%20Zardari's%20party%20appeared%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20the%20economic%20reforms%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Sharif%20government%2C%20including%20raising%20fuel%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20year's%20election%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20contested%20as%20rivals%20but%20later%20agreed%20to%20hold%20talks%20to%20%26quot%3Bsave%20the%20country%20from%20political%20instability%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Sharif.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708490460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2grve2mg_bilawal-bhutto-shehbaz-sharif_625x300_12_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-elections-imran-khan-at-midnight-meet-shehbaz-sharif-bilawal-bhutto-seal-power-sharing-deal-5097969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20two%20old-guard%20political%20parties%20agreed%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%20a%20move%20that%20breaks%20an%20almost%20two-week%20deadlock%20and%20likely%20keeps%20jailed%20former%20premier%20Imran%20Khan's%20party%20out%20of%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-elections-imran-khan-at-midnight-meet-shehbaz-sharif-bilawal-bhutto-seal-power-sharing-deal-5097969%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-elections-imran-khan-at-midnight-meet-shehbaz-sharif-bilawal-bhutto-seal-power-sharing-deal-5097969%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-elections-imran-khan-at-midnight-meet-shehbaz-sharif-bilawal-bhutto-seal-power-sharing-deal-5097969%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22tit