20million%20in%20the%20accounts%20of%20Zee%20Entertainment%20Enterprises%20Ltd.%2C%20dealing%20another%20blow%20to%20the%20embattled%20media%20firm%20less%20than%20a%20month%20after%20its%20merger%20with%20Sony%20Group%20Corp's%20local%20unit%20collapsed.%20Zee%20shares%20fell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20investigation%20into%20the%20Zee%20founders%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%2C%20or%20Sebi%2C%20found%20that%20about%2020%20billion%20rupees%20(%24241%20million)%20may%20have%20been%20diverted%20from%20the%20company%2C%20said%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20the%20information%20is%20not%20public%20yet.%20That's%20roughly%20ten%20times%20of%20what%20was%20initially%20estimated%20by%20Sebi%20investigators%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZee%20shares%20slid%20as%20much%20as%2015%25%20in%20Mumbai%20trading%2C%20the%20most%20in%20a%20month%2C%20before%20paring%20some%20of%20the%20losses.%20Benchmark%20S%26amp%3BP%20BSE%20Sensex%20was%20marginally%20up%2C%20according%20to%20data%20compiled%20by%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20found%20missing%20is%20not%20final%20and%20may%20change%20after%20Sebi%20reviews%20the%20responses%20from%20the%20company%20executives%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20The%20regulator%20has%20been%20calling%20in%20senior%20officials%20at%20Zee%20including%20founders%2C%20Subhash%20Chandra%2C%20his%20son%20Punit%20Goenka%20and%20some%20board%20members%20to%20explain%20their%20stance%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Sebi%20representative%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20an%20emailed%20request%20for%20comments.%20A%20Zee%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20fund%20diversion%20but%20said%20in%20an%20email%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20in%20the%20process%20of%20providing%20all%20the%20comments%2C%20information%20or%20explanation%20requested%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20markets%20regulator%20in%20the%20ongoing%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESebi's%20latest%20findings%20add%20to%20Mr%20Goenka's%20woes%2C%20as%20the%20Zee%20CEO%20tries%20to%20reassure%20investors%20after%20its%20%2410%20billion%20merger%20plan%20with%20Sony%20fell%20apart.%20The%20transaction%2C%20two%20years%20in%20the%20making%2C%20was%20terminated%20in%20January%20after%20a%20months-long%20stalemate%20on%20who'll%20lead%20the%20new%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZee%20is%20re-engaging%20with%20Sony%20to%20assess%20if%20the%20merger%20can%20be%20revived%20but%20major%20differences%20persist%2C%20The%20Economic%20Times%20reported%20Tuesday%2C%20without%20saying%20where%20it%20got%20the%20information%20from.%20The%20Indian%20media%20firm%20clarified%20in%20a%20late-evening%20filing%20Tuesday%20that%20it%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20any%20negotiations%20to%20revive%20the%20Sony%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuch%20Wrangling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulatory%20probe%20into%20the%20father-and-son%20duo's%20alleged%20financial%20improprieties%20has%20led%20to%20much%20wrangling%20between%20Sony%20and%20Zee%20since%20mid-2023.%20It%20made%20Sony%20wary%20of%20letting%20Goenka%20helm%20the%20merged%20entity%20while%20Mr%20Goenka%20refused%20to%20give%20in%20as%20the%20CEO%20spot%20was%20promised%20to%20him%20in%20the%202021%20merger%20pact.%20The%20standoff%20ultimately%20led%20to%20Sony%20scuttling%20the%20deal%20in%20January.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESebi%2C%20in%20an%20order%20in%20August%2C%20barred%20Zee%20founders%20-%20Mr%20Chandra%20and%20Mr%20Goenka%20-%20from%20holding%20executive%20or%20director%20positions%20in%20any%20listed%20firm%20after%20finding%20that%20they%20had%20%26quot%3Babused%20their%20position%26quot%3B%20and%20siphoned%20off%20funds%20%26quot%3Bfor%20their%20own%20benefit.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZee%20appealed%20Sebi's%20order%20in%20a%20higher%20appellate%20authority%20and%20got%20a%20partial%20reprieve%20in%20Octobe