e-54310.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fjust-like-his-name-sachin-tendulkars-special-message-as-virat-kohli-anushka-sharma-welcome-their-son-akaay%2Farticleshow%2F107868362.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20on%20Tuesday%20joyfully%20revealed%20on%20social%20media%20that%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20Anushka%20Sharma%20welcomed%20a%20baby%20boy%20on%20February%2015.%20Joining%20in%20the%20celebration%2C%20cricket%20icon%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20extended%20his%20congratulations%20through%20his%20social%20media%20platform.%20This%20joyous%20occasion%20adds%20to%20the%20couple's%20happiness%20as%20they%20are%20already%20proud%20parents%20to%20a%20three-year-old%20daughter%20named%20Vamika.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fjust-like-his-name-sachin-tendulkars-special-message-as-virat-kohli-anushka-sharma-welcome-their-son-akaay%2Farticleshow%2F107868362.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM-Kisan%2C%20Budget%20Hike%2C%20Kisan%20Rail%3A%20Government%20Sources%20List%20Pro-Farmer%20Steps%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20farmers%20resume%20their%20march%20to%20Delhi%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20Centre%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20taken%20several%20pro-farmer%20steps%20during%20its%2010%20years%20in%20power%2C%20including%20a%20hike%20in%20budget%20allocation%20for%20agriculture%2C%20assistance%20under%20the%20PM-Kisan%20scheme%20and%20the%20Kisan%20credit%20card%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20budget%20allocation%20has%20been%20increased%20by%205.26%20times%20in%202023-24%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20year%202013-14%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20budgets%20in%20the%20past%20decade%20have%20put%20emphasis%20on%20promoting%20agriculture%20sector%20through%20technology%20so%20that%20farmers%20get%20comprehensive%20benefits%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20has%20been%20transferring%20Rs%206%2C000%20annually%20to%20the%20bank%20account%20of%20farmers%20since%20December%202018.%20%26quot%3BAn%20amount%20of%20Rs.%202.81%20lakh%20crore%20has%20been%20given%20in%20cash%20to%20more%20than%2011%20crore%20farmers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20also%20listed%20steps%20such%20as%20setting%20up%20new%20farmer%20producer%20organisations%20to%20provide%20support%20to%20small%20farmers%20and%20an%20infrastructure%20fund%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20sources%20put%20forward%20arguments%20on%20how%20it%20has%20worked%20to%20increase%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20for%20several%20crops.%20MSP%20is%20a%20price%20fixed%20by%20the%20government%20and%20is%20aimed%20at%20protecting%20farmers%20from%20distress%20sale%20of%20their%20produce.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20reasons%20behind%20talks%20between%20the%20farmers%20and%20the%20Centre%20falling%20through%20is%20a%20disagreement%20over%20which%20MSP%20formula%20to%20follow.%20The%20farmers%20say%20the%20government's%20conditions%20to%20provide%20MSP%20would%20only%20provide%20subsistence%20and%20not%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20has%20increased%20MSP%20for%20mandated%20kharif%2C%20rabi%20and%20other%20commercial%20crops%20with%20a%20return%20of%20at%20least%2050%20per%20cent%20over%20all%20India%20weighted%20average%20cost%20of%20production%20from%202018-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20added%20that%20the%20government's%20procurement%20from%20farmers%20has%20also%20increased.%20%26quot%3BThe%20procurement%20under%20PSS%20(Price%20Support%20Scheme)%20during%20the%20year%202021-22%2C%20a%20quantity%20of%2031%2C82%2C591.64%20MT%20of%20pulses%2C%20oilseeds%20and%20copra%20having%20MSP%20value%20of%20Rs.%2017%2C478.31%20crore%20benefiting%2014%2C68%2C699%20farmers%20and%20during%202022-23%20season%20a%20quantity%20of%2040%2C02%2C057.73%20MT%20of%20pulses%2C%20oilseeds%20%26amp%3B%20copra%20having%20MSP%20Value%20of%20Rs.%2022%2C728.23%20crore%20benefiting%2017%2C27%2C663%20farmers%20had%20been%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Kisan%20Credit%20Card%20scheme%2C%20the%20sources%20said%2C%20the%20government%20has%20earmarked%20a%20credit%20outlay%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20crore%20to%20farmers%20in%202023-24.%20The%20benefits%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20they%20said%2C%20have%20also%20been%20extended%20to%20animal%20husbandry%20and%20fisheries%20farmers%20so%20that%20they%20can%20meet%20short-term%20working%20capital%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20sources%20also%20underlined%20its%20emphasis%20on%20millet%20production%20by%20listing%20how%20it%20used%20national%20and%20international%20forums%20to%20showcase%20the%20benefits%20of%20millet%20consumption%20and%20step%20up%20research%20into%20its%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre's%20steps%20to%20address%20the%20air%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%20were%20also%20put%20forward.%20%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20support%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%20to%20address%20air%20pollution%20due%20to%20crop%20residue%20burning%2C%20funds%20amounting%20to%20Rs.3138.56%20crores%20have%20been%20released%20to%20these%20states%20during%20the%20period%20from%202018-19%20to%202022-23%2C%20for%20crop%20residue%20management%20through%20mechanization%20interventions%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20government%20explained%20how%20the%20Centre%20had%20expanded%20crop%20insurance%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Fasal%20Bima%20Yojana.%20To%20bolster%20their%20points%2C%20they%20asserted%20how%20food%20grain%20production%20increased%20from%20265.05%20million%20tonnes%20in%202013-14%20to%20329.69%20million%20tonnes%20in%202022-23%20--%20the%20highest%20ever.%C2%A0The%20Kisan%20Rail%20initiative%20was%20started%20to%20save%20produce%20of%20farmers%20from%20getting%20spoiled%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708487040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fv5odft4_farmers-protest_625x300_21_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-pm-kisan-budget-hike-kisan-rail-government-sources-list-pro-farmer-steps-5097842%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20before%20farmers%20resume%20their%20march%20to%20Delhi%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20Centre%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20taken%20several%20pro-farmer%20steps%20during%20its%2010%20years%20in%20power%2C%20including%20a%20hike%20in%20budget%20allocation%20for%20agriculture%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-pm-kisan-budget-hike-kisan-rail-government-sources-list-pro-farmer-steps-5097842%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-pm-kisan-budget-hike-kisan-rail-government-sources-list-pro-farmer-steps-5097842%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-pm-kisan-budget-hike-kisan-rail-government-sources-list-pro-farmer-steps-5097842%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20compares%20his%20legal%20woes%20to%20late%20Russian%20dissident%20Navalny%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708486899000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107868645%2Cimgsize-28972.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-compares-legal-woes-to-late-russian-dissident-navalny%2Farticleshow%2F107868308.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22