t%20by%20the%20time%20they%20could%20do%20anything%2C%20one%20of%20the%20lions%20had%20already%20fatally%20wounded%20him%2C%20the%20university%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20lion%20has%20since%20been%20put%20down%2C%20the%20statement%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Olawuyi%20was%20a%20veterinary%20technologist%20who%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Btaking%20care%20of%20the%20lions%20since%20they%20were%20born%20on%20campus%20about%20nine%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20university's%20spokesman%20Abiodun%20Olarewaju%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68345157%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTragically%2C%20the%20male%20lion%20killed%20the%20man%20who%20had%20been%20feeding%20them.%20We%20never%20knew%20what%20came%20over%20the%20male%20lion%20that%20it%20had%20to%20attack%20%5Bhim%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Olarewaju%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university's%20vice-chancellor%2C%20Professor%20Adebayo%20Simeon%20Bamire%2C%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bsaddened%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20incident%20and%20ordered%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20students'%20union%20leader%2C%20Abbas%20Akinremi%2C%20described%20the%20incident%20as%20unfortunate%20and%20said%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20caused%20by%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20error%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20zookeeper%20had%20forgotten%20to%20lock%20the%20door%20after%20feeding%20the%20lions.%20Mr%20Akinremi%20also%20paid%20tribute%20to%20Mr%20Olawuyi.%20He%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20and%20humble%20man%2C%20who%20attended%20to%20us%20nicely%20whenever%20we%20went%20to%20the%20zoo%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbba%20Gandu%2C%20who%20has%20been%20feeding%20lions%20for%20more%20than%2050%20years%20at%20a%20zoo%20in%20Kano%20in%20northern%20Nigeria%2C%20also%20described%20the%20incident%20as%20unfortunate%20and%20said%20more%20safety%20measures%20were%20needed.%20%26quot%3BThis%20incident%20wouldn't%20in%20any%20way%20affect%20me%20personally%20as%20feeding%20lions%20is%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do%20until%20I%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Gandu.%20He%20added%20that%20his%20worst%20experience%20was%20when%20a%20baboon%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20feed%20bit%20his%20finger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fus-zoo-extracts-70-coins-from-alligator-urges-visitors-to-avoid-tossing-money-in-water-5092445%5C%22%3EUS%20Zoo%20Extracts%2070%20Coins%20From%20Alligator%2C%20Urges%20Visitors%20To%20Avoid%20Tossing%20Money%20in%20Water%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20Nigerians%20on%20social%20media%20also%20shared%20graphic%20images%20of%20the%20mauling%20at%20the%20university%20in%20Osun%20state.%20The%20university%20community%20is%20in%20mourning.%20As%20per%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20delegation%20has%20also%20gone%20to%20the%20family%20of%20Mr%20Olawuyi%20to%20offer%20their%20condolences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20similar%20incident%20in%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-enters-lions-enclosure-in-andhra-zoo-to-click-selfie-mauled-to-death-5064102%5C%22%3Ea%20man%20was%20mauled%20to%20death%20by%20a%20lion%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20Tirupati%20zoo.%20Authorities%20at%20the%20Sri%20Venkateswara%20Zoological%20Park%20said%20the%20man%2C%20identified%20as%2038-year-old%20Prahlad%20Gujjar%20from%20Alwar%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20had%20entered%20the%20enclosure%20after%20getting%20into%20an%20unauthorised%20section%20that%20was%20not%20open%20to%20the%20public.%20He%20had%20reportedly%20ignored%20a%20caretaker's%20warnings%20to%20back%20off%2C%20climbed%20a%20fence%20that%20is%20over%2025%20feet%20tall%20and%20jumped%20into%20the%20enclosure.%20The%20lion%2C%20named%20Dongalpur%2C%20mauled%20Gujjar%20to%20death%20before%20the%20caretaker%20could%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%22