levels%20are%20soaring%2C%20it%20may%20suggest%20that%20workers%20are%20facing%20challenges%20in%20sustaining%20their%20living%20standards%20and%20may%20be%20merely%20surviving%20rather%20than%20thriving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20data%20also%20hampers%20the%20measurement%20of%20how%20an%20economy%20consumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20trouble%20is%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20a%20consumption%20survey.%20There%20was%20a%20consumption%20survey%20for%202017-18%2C%20but%20the%20government%20ditched%20that%20one%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20results.%20A%20leaked%20version%20of%20that%20survey%20showed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fconsumer-sending-fall-rural-demand-nso-report%5C%22%3Erural%20consumption%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20actually%20fallen%20over%20that%20six-year%20period%2C%20from%202011-12%20to%202017-18.%20And%20since%20then%20they%20have%20not%20had%20a%20consumption%20survey.%20They%E2%80%99re%20supposed%20to%20be%20doing%20one%20now%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99ll%20not%20get%20those%20results%20for%20at%20least%20another%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20renowned%20development%20economist%20Jayati%20Ghosh%20said%2C%20while%20speaking%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20whether%20Indian%20workers%20are%20thriving%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fblogs%2Fmyview%2Findia-under-pm-modi-poised-to-become-a-5-trillion-economy-in-5-years%2F%5C%22%3Egrowing%20GDP%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20merely%20surviving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20why%20would%20you%20not%20do%20a%20consumption%20survey%3F%20Because%20those%20surveys%20tell%20us%20how%20many%20poor%20people%20are%20there%20are%20in%20the%20country%2C%20where%20they%20are%2C%20what%20they%20do%3B%20they%20%5Bthese%20surveys%5D%20tell%20us%20about%20distribution%2C%20because%20these%20give%20us%20some%20indication%20of%20who%20can%20consume%20what%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20other%20survey%20which%20is%20%5Balso%5D%20a%20better%20indicator%20is%20the%20labour%20force%20survey.%20The%20government%20has%20allowed%20that%20survey%20to%20continue%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20long%20they%20will%2C%20because%20that%20has%20also%20not%20shown%20good%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20further%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20%5BThe%20labour%20force%20survey%5D%20shows%20us%20that%20real%20wages%20are%20more%20or%20less%20stagnating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNote%20that%20these%20are%20average%20real%20wages%20and%20these%20can%20get%20distorted%20at%20the%20upper%20end%2C%20and%20make%20it%20look%20higher.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20if%20we%20really%20want%20to%20know%20how%20workers%20are%20doing%2C%20we%20should%20be%20looking%20at%20the%20median%20wages%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20many%20countries%20do.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20look%20at%20the%20median%20wages.%20That%20is%2C%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20distribution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20average%20wages%20are%20stagnating%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20quite%20possible%20that%20the%20median%20wages%20have%20actually%20come%20down%20in%20real%20terms.%20Some%20people%20are%20actually%20working%20on%20this%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20the%20average%20can%20be%20skewed%20by%20outliers%2C%20especially%20if%20there%20are%20significant%20income%20disparities%20within%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funpaid-labour-on-the-rise-muslims-not-looking-for-work-what-the-plfs-data-reveals%5C%22%3EUnpaid%20Labour%20on%20the%20Rise%2C%20Muslims%20Not%20Looking%20for%20Work%3A%20What%20the%20PLFS%20Data%20Reveals%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20interesting%20sets%20of%20data%20%E2%80%93%20vehicle%20registrations%20and%20provident%20fund%20distribution%20by%20large%2C%20medium%20and%20small%20firms%20%E2%80%93%20that%20could%20give%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20economic%20well-being%20of%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20used%20to%20create%20the%20charts%20below%20is%20as%20of%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFluctuations%20in%20two-wheelers%2C%20steady%20growth%20in%20hybrid%20and%20electric%20vehicles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVehicle%20registrations%20are%20also%20considered%20a%20proxy%20for%20retail%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo-wheeler%20sales%20data%20are%20often%20considered%20a%20key%20indicator%20of%20consumption%20demand%2C%20especially%20in%20countries%20like%20India%20where%20they%20are%20a%20popular%20mode%20of%20transportation.%20They%20indicate%20the%20purchasing%20capacity%20of%20the%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20shows%20that%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%2C%20registrations%20of%20two-wheelers%20dropped%20to%20161%2C314%20units%20in%20May%202020%20and%20kept%20fluctuating%20until%20January%202023.%20They%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20recovering%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20on%20September%2030%2C%202023%2C%20they%20stood%20at%201.31%20million%20units%2C%20higher%20than%201.16%20million%20units%20in%20the%20same%20period%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20clearly%20reaches%20its%20peak%20in%20the%20month%20of%20November%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20noteworthy%20here%20is%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20dip%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20the%20fluctuations%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20registrations%20of%20hybrid%20vehicles%20within%20the%20renewable%20category%20and%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fh8Wd8%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Two-wheeler%20sales%3A%20A%20rollercoaster%20ride%20from%20lockdown%20lows%20to%20recovery%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVehicle%20registrations%20in%20the%20renewable%20category%20(see%20below)%20show%20a%20steady%20rise.%20As%20earlier%20mentioned%2C%20this%20category%20includes%20hybrid%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20hybrid%20vehicles%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fauto.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpassenger-vehicle%2Fare-hybrid-vehicles-better-than-electric-vehicles%2F104908025%5C%22%3Etend%20to%20be%20more%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20compared%20to%20their%20conventional%20counterparts.%20Hybrid%20cars%20also%20require%20more%20maintenance%20than%20the%20conventional%20ones.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20question%20is%2C%20how%20many%20people%20from%20the%20middle%20class%20and%20lower-middle%20class%20can%20afford%20buying%20hybrid%20models%20of%20cars%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20luxury%20cars%20are%20also%20doing%20well%20and%20not%20just%20the%20EVs.%20EVs%20are%20definitely%20expensive.%20And%20so%20are%20hybrid%20%5Bvehicles%5D.%20They%20are%20all%20much%20more%20%5Bexpensive%5D%20than%20the%20regular%20%5Bvehicles%5D.%20But%20all%20luxury%20vehicles%20are%20doing%20well.%20So%2C%20that%20tells%20you%20exactly%20who%E2%80%99s%20gaining%20from%20all%20this%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ghosh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Frenewables%2Findia-sees-over-120-growth-in-evs-hybrid-vehicles-surge-400%2Farticleshow%2F102895037.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3ENews%20agency%20IANS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20a%20report%20by%20Cyber%20Media%20Research%2C%20said%20that%20India%20saw%20a%20120%25%20growth%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202023%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20400%25%20surge%20in%20hybrid%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FvGlm2%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Vehicle%20registrations%20within%20the%20renewable%20category%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%20the%20chart%20below%2C%20registrations%20of%20electric%20(battery%20operated)%20vehicles%20peaked%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20had%20started.%20After%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20demand%20has%20consistently%20risen.%20Their%20adoption%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20over%20120%20million%20people%20in%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fdata%2Fdata-over-12-crore-indians-lost-their-jobs-during-the-coronavirus-lockdown-in-april%2Farticle61660110.ece%5C%22%3Elost%20their%20jobs%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20indicate%20stark%20economic%20disparities%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FOD2bc%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Electric%20vehicles%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20than%20EV%20sales%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenergy.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpower%2Findias-ev-sales-surge-to-1-5-million-in-2023-up-50-report%2F106971357%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20revving%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20despite%20concerns%20over%20a%20lack%20of%20charging%20stations%20and%20policy%20roadblocks.%20But%20again%2C%20which%20segment%20of%20the%20population%20buys%20EVs%20and%20hybrid%20vehicles%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20remarkable%20surge%20in%20luxury%20cars%20shows%20that%20the%20purchasing%20power%20of%20these%20buyers%20has%20grown%20exponentially%2C%20and%20they%20are%20not%20hesitating%20to%20spend%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmultimedia%2Faudio%2Fwhat-is-driving-indias-luxury-car-market-boom%2Farticle67344022.ece%5C%22%3EState%20of%20The%20Economy%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20