ventory-days-for-consumer-goods-as-low-demand-causes-supply-chain-congestion%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%20that%20persistent%20low%20demand%20in%20the%20FMCG%20sector%20is%20causing%20supply%20chain%20congestion%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20inventory%20days%2C%20with%20stocks%20accumulating%20at%20distributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20big%20companies%20such%20as%20Hindustan%20Unilever%20and%20Dabur%20have%20also%20said%20that%20the%20rural%20markets%20are%20lagging%20urban.%20Many%20have%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Frural-demand-revival-what-new-data-tells-us-11698085155203.html%5C%22%3Eraised%20doubts%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20a%20revival%20in%20rural%20demand%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedium-sized%20firms%20saw%20sharp%20decline%20in%20PF%20contributions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProvident%20Fund%20(PF)%20contributions%20by%20large%2C%20medium%20and%20small%20firms%20reflect%20how%20people%20save%20in%20an%20economy.%20It%20could%20also%20be%20an%20indicator%20of%20social%20security%20within%20an%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20data%20is%20a%20good%20indicator%20on%20how%20workers%20are%20doing%20in%20an%20economy.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20you%20register%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%2C%20for%20the%20EPF%2C%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20do%20anything%20with%20monthly%20payment%2C%20especially%20when%20you%20change%20jobs.%20%5BMany%20time%5D%20workers%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20%5Bthey%20have%20an%20EPF%5D%2C%20and%20it%20gets%20dropped%20from%20their%20pay%20when%20they%20join%20another%20firm%2C%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20portable.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20carry%20it%20with%20them.%20So%2C%20they%20actually%20lose.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20tax%20on%20their%20wage%20rather%20than%20actually%20savings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ghosh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecondly%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20doing%20the%20surveys%20that%20they%20should%20be.%20There%20was%20an%20all-India%20Debt%20and%20Investment%20survey%2C%20which%20was%20due%2C%20which%20would%20give%20us%20an%20idea%20about%20household%20savings.%20And%20how%20much%20dissavings%20happens%20at%20the%20lower%20level.%20So%2C%20they%20%5Bthe%20government%5D%20are%20not%20collecting%20the%20important%20data%20that%20wold%20give%20us%20this%20information%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20what%20you%E2%80%99ve%20just%20described%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20PF%20of%20the%20large%20firms%20versus%20the%20others%20%5Bmedium%20and%20small%20firms%5D%2C%20it%20speaks%20very%20much%20of%20the%20broader%20picture%20that%20is%20coming%20out%20of%20corporate%20profitability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20professor%20pointed%20out%20a%20report%20which%20said%20that%2090%25%20of%20the%20corporate%20profit%20in%20India%20was%20made%20by%20the%20top%20few%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20top%2020%20profit%20generators%20in%20India%20(%E2%80%9Cthe%20Leviathans%E2%80%9D)%20now%20account%20for%2090%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20corporate%20profits.%20Beyond%20dominating%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20profit%20pool%2C%20the%20Leviathans%20also%20reinvest%20these%20profits%20far%20more%20efficiently%20back%20into%20their%20businesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarcellus.in%2Fblogs%2Findias-top-20-leviathans-awe-inspiring-dominance%2F%5C%22%3EMarcellus%20Investment%20Managers%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%202020.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20reduced%20profitability%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20negative%20profitability.%20And%20we%20know%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20churning%20in%20the%20small%20and%20micro%20enterprises.%20Some%20are%20closing%20down%20and%20then%20people%20start%20some