3E%2C%20launched%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20is%20one%20of%20several%20similar%20initiatives%20that%20have%20rolled%20out%20in%20cities%20across%20the%20US%20in%20recent%20years%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-works-red-state-blue-state-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevidence%20shows%20they%20are%20working%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20St.%20Louis%2C%20recipients%20were%20chosen%20from%20over%205%2C500%20applicants.%20In%20December%2C%20they%20received%20their%20first%20%24500%2C%20which%20is%20issued%20via%20a%20debit%20card%20and%20can%20be%20spent%20on%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20the%20city%20is%20given%20reports%20from%20the%20card%20issuer%20with%20broad%20spending%20category%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20categories%20where%20we%20see%20spending%20is%20pretty%20much%20where%20we%20anticipated%2C%26quot%3B%20Adam%20Layne%2C%20the%20St.%20Louis%20city%20treasurer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20That%20includes%20utilities%2C%20groceries%2C%20and%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-simple-solution-homelessness-researcher-study-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebills%2C%20like%20rent%20or%20a%20mortgage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20outstanding%20debt.%20Food%20and%20nutrition%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELayne%20said%20some%20recipients%20said%20they%20were%20one%20car%20payment%20away%20from%20losing%20their%20car%20%E2%80%94%20which%20would%20mean%20being%20unable%20to%20get%20to%20work%20or%20get%20their%20kids%20to%20school%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20the%20payment%20helped%20them%20avoid%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSimilarly%2C%20we%20had%20folks%20that%20were%20one%20missed%20payment%20away%20from%20being%20out%20of%20their%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20recipients%20have%20used%20the%20basic%20income%20payments%20to%20get%20out%20of%20predatory%20payday%20cycle%20lending%2C%20where%20they%20were%20paying%20500%25%20interest%20on%20a%20%24100%20loan%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20notable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-income-gbi-arlington-virginia-affordable-housing-education-job-security-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20categories%3C%2Fa%3E%20include%20phone%20and%20internet%20bills%20as%20well%20as%20books%20and%20school%20supplies%2C%20Layne%20said%20the%20data%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20participating%20families%20were%20chosen%20in%20November%20based%20on%20just%20a%20few%20criteria.%20They%20had%20to%20be%20residents%20of%20St.%20Louis%2C%20have%20a%20school-age%20child%2C%20and%20have%20had%20a%20negative%20financial%20impact%20from%20the%20pandemic.%20They%20also%20needed%20to%20make%20less%20than%20170%25%20of%20the%20federal%20poverty%20level%3B%20for%20a%20family%20of%20two%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20that%20would%20be%20%2433%2C524.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20program%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20last%20for%2018%20months%2C%20is%20primarily%20funded%20by%20money%20St.%20Louis%20received%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stlouis-mo.gov%2Fgovernment%2Fdepartments%2Fmayor%2Finitiatives%2Fgbi.cfm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Rescue%20Plan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Twitter%20cofounder%20Jack%20Dorsey's%20%23startsmall%20philanthropic%20initiative%20also%20contributed%2C%20allowing%20the%20program%20to%20take%20on%20an%20extra%20100%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELayne%20said%20the%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20program%20took%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20planning%20and%20coordinating%20with%20partners%2C%20including%20researchers%20at%20Washington%20University%20in%20St.%20Louis.%20He%20said%20they%20are%20committed%20to%20gathering%20quantitative%20and%20qualitative%20data%20to%20measure%20the%20succe