0with%20Generative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20spearheaded%20by%20Fran%C3%A7ois%20Candelon%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20and%20senior%20partner%20at%20consulting%20company%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study's%20findings%20are%20back%20in%20the%20news%20this%20week%20after%20Candelon%20sat%20down%20with%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fthe-best-way-to-work-with-ai-a-study-may-reveal-the-answers-36e2a166%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExecutive%20Insights%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20discuss%20generative%20AI%20in%20the%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECandelon%20partnered%20with%20talent%20from%20top%20universities%20like%20MIT%2C%20Wharton%2C%20Harvard%20Business%20School%2C%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Warwick%2C%20and%20used%20his%20consulting%20company's%20own%20employees%20to%20execute%20the%20experiment%2C%20which%20he%20told%20The%20Journal%20was%20inspired%20by%20his%20desire%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20humans%20and%20AI%20can%20work%20together%20to%20help%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20than%20750%20study%20participants%20were%20given%20real%20tasks%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20product%20innovation%26quot%3B%20assignments.%20The%20participants%20were%20instructed%20to%20use%20OpenAI%20tool%20GPT-4%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20help%20them%20with%20tasks%20like%20pitching%20the%20shoe%20concepts%20to%20their%20boss%2C%20coming%20up%20with%20focus%20group%20questions%2C%20and%20executing%20a%20successful%20social%20media%20rollout%2C%20Candelon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%20people%20using%20AI%20faired%20much%20better%20than%20those%20working%20without%20it%20when%20it%20came%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zer-uses-ai-create-content-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreative%20product%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%20tasks.%20About%2090%25%20of%20the%20participants%20improved%20their%20performance%20when%20using%20AI%20for%20any%20task%20involving%20ideation%20and%20content%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParticipants%20also%20converged%20on%20a%20performance%20level%20that%20was%2040%25%20higher%20than%20those%20working%20on%20the%20same%20task%20without%20GPT-4%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20benefits%20were%20seen%20when%20people%20didn't%20try%20to%20change%20or%20improve%20the%20technology's%20output%20suggestions%2C%20accepting%20GPT-4's%20suggestions%20as%20is%2C%20the%20study%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20still%20some%20tasks%20where%20humans%20have%20the%20edge.%20People's%20problem-solving%20skills%20far%20outweigh%20the%20help%20offered%20by%20AI%2C%20Candelon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%20generative%20AI%20actually%20persuaded%20several%20participants%20to%20accept%20GPT's%20misleading%20output%2C%20even%20when%20they%20had%20been%20briefed%20on%20the%20possibility%20of%20wrong%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParticipants%20who%20used%20AI%20for%20problem-solving%20tasks%20performed%2023%25%20worse%20than%20those%20who%20didn't%20use%20the%20tool%20at%20all%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bdouble-edged%20sword%26quot%3B%20that%20is%20generative%20AI%2C%20with%20its%20%26quot%3Brelatively%20uniform%20output%2C%26quot%3B%20can%20also%20reduce%20a%20group's%20diversity%20of%20thought%20by%2041%25%2C%20the%20study%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Candelon%20stressed%20to%20The%20Journal%20that%20AI%20is%20exceedingly%20powerful%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20unavoidable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20this%20famous%20quote%20saying%20that%20humans%20won't%20get%20replaced%20by%20AI.%20They%20will%20get%20replaced%20by%20humans%20using%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECandelon%20said%20the%20study%20shows%20that%20data%20will%20become%20even%20more%20important%20with%20generative%20AI%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20forcing%20people%20to%20revisit%20their%20workflows%20and%20figure%20out%20places%20for%20human%20and%20AI%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-boosts-workplace-creativity-cant-match-peoples-problem-solving-skills-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708474874000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65170add3fb8f400198ad734%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-boosts-workplace-creativity-cant-match-peoples-problem-solving-skills-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20study%20on%20generative%20AI%20in%20the%20workplace%20found%20that%20the%20technology%20can%20actually%20lead%20people%20to%20make%20mistakes%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20problem-solving.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A79%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-boosts-workplace-creativity-cant-match-peoples-problem-solving-skills-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20vetoes%20UN's%20Gaza%20ceasefire%20resolution%2C%20again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708474845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107865192%2Cimgsize-1559248.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-vetoes-uns-gaza-ceasefire-resolution-again%2Farticleshow%2F107865182.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107865182.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20vetoed%20a%20draft%20UN%20Security%20Council%20resolution%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20blocking%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire.%20Instead%2C%20the%20US%20proposed%20a%20rival%20resolution%20for