e's%20first%20floor.%20%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20visited%20on%20a%20Friday%20morning%2C%20I%20expected%20the%20lounge%20to%20be%20crowded%20with%20weekend%20travelers.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20shortage%20of%20places%20to%20sit%20and%20relax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two-story%20lounge%20had%20sitting%20areas%20upstairs%20and%20downstairs.%20The%20first%20level%20also%20had%20a%20bar%2C%20a%20restaurant%2C%20a%20coworking%20space%2C%20a%20family%20area%20with%20places%20to%20sit%20and%20play%2C%20and%20an%20arcade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20never%20thought%20I'd%20be%20able%20to%20blast%20music%20in%20an%20airport.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20presses%20a%20button%20on%20a%20vintage%20marshall%20juke%20box%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b9211dac2de4f17ee5d2dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20vintage%20Jukebox%20in%20the%20arcade.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20arcade's%20volume%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20surprising%20things%20to%20me.%20Designed%20like%20a%20retro%20speakeasy%2C%20the%20hidden%20room%20was%20behind%20a%20soundproof%20curtain%20and%20housed%20a%20vintage%20Marshall%20Jukebox%20filled%20with%20CDs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20room%20was%20soundproof%2C%20I%20could%20blast%20tunes%20as%20loud%20as%20a%20nightclub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20danced%20and%20played%20pinball%20while%20cranking%20to%20classic%20hits%20like%20%26quot%3BMove%20Your%20Feet%26quot%3B%20by%20Junior%20Senior%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20how%20helpful%20it%20would%20be%20to%20release%20some%20energy%20before%20a%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20just%20around%20the%20corner%20was%20a%20quiet%20spa%20offering%20complimentary%20facials.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20a%20facial%20treatment%20room%20with%20wood%20floors%20and%20cabinets%20and%20a%20leather%20beige%20chair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cb9960f533b039a882ee9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20a%20spa%20treatment%20room.%20%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20three%20years%20of%20travel%20reporting%2C%20I%20never%20thought%20I'd%20receive%20a%20facial%20at%20an%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20was%20in%20awe%20when%20I%20found%20a%20serene%20spa%20on%20the%20first%20floor%20with%20meditation%20spaces%20and%20treatment%20rooms%20where%20guests%20can%20book%2030-minute%20complimentary%20facials.%20There%20was%20a%20range%20of%20options%20made%20for%20air%20travelers%20with%20components%20that%20decreased%20inflammation%20and%20hydrated%20the%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20with%20a%20treatment%20called%20the%20Illuminator%2C%20which%20gets%20rid%20of%20flare-ups%20and%20purifies%20skin%20with%20red%20and%20blue%20lights.%20It%20was%20as%20calming%20and%20effective%20as%20any%20facial%20you'd%20expect%20from%20a%20high-end%20spa%2C%20and%20I%20left%20with%20a%20glow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20also%20surprised%20to%20find%20private%20suites%20where%20travelers%20spend%20at%20least%20%242%2C000%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20in%20what%20is%20essentially%20a%20luxury%20hotel%20room.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20a%20vibrant%20suite%20with%20a%20living%20room%20space%20on%20the%20left%2C%20a%20table%20with%20four%20chairs%20on%20the%20right%2C%20and%20a%20bar%20with%20a%20mirrored%20bar%20in%20the%20back%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cba5696fcb546d2d4f24b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20one%20of%20the%20private%20suites.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C