the%20Calcutta%20high%20court.%20One%20BJP%20MLA%20allegedly%20called%20a%20Sikh%20IPS%20officer%20present%20there%20a%20%E2%80%9CKhalistani%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20criticised%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20Section%20144%20%E2%80%93%20which%20restricts%20public%20assembly%20%E2%80%93%20calling%20it%20unnecessary%20and%20contributing%20to%20the%20rising%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20after%20police%20initially%20blocked%20delegations%20led%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%E2%80%99s%20Brinda%20Karat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20MLAs%20led%20by%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20visit%20Sandeshkhali%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdhikari%2C%20finally%20entering%20Sandeshkhali%20on%20his%20third%20attempt%2C%20met%20with%20the%20villagers%2C%20listened%20to%20their%20concerns%20about%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20and%20land%20grabbing%20and%20offered%20his%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20visited%20the%20home%20of%20Bikash%20Sinha%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20who%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20last%20week%20and%20then%20re-arrested%20immediately%20after%20apparently%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Cold%20case%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20his%20visit%2C%20Adhikari%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20finally%20spoken%20to%20the%20victims%20here.%20Women%20have%20been%20sexually%20assaulted%2C%20and%20tribals%20have%20had%20their%20lands%20forcefully%20taken.%20I%20urged%20them%20to%20pursue%20justice%20through%20the%20legal%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20absconding%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShahjahan%20is%20still%20roaming%20around%20here.%20If%20he%20attempts%20to%20escape%20to%20Bangladesh%2C%20he%20must%20be%20apprehended%20forcefully.%20The%20BSF%20%5BBorder%20Security%20Force%5D%