ia%2C%20where%20there%E2%80%99s%20greater%20gender%20equality%20and%20women%20have%20more%20access%20to%20cash.%20Over%20time%2C%20sales%20began%20to%20increase%20nationwide.%20To%20date%2C%20they%20have%20sold%20over%20three%20million%20stoves%20across%20India%2C%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20and%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20a%20factory%20in%20Vadodara%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20with%20over%20500%20employees.%20Ankit%E2%80%99s%20vision%20is%20to%20reach%2020%20million%20households%20by%202030.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20keep%20designing%20products%20that%20increase%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20rural%20households.%20I%20also%20aspire%20to%20reach%20more%20customers%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%20point%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Greenway%20Grameen%20Infra)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708435145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342452%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Greenway%20Grameen%20Infra%2C%20co-founded%20by%20Ankit%20Mathur%20and%20Neha%20Juneja%2C%20innovated%20the%20'Smart%20Stove'%20as%20an%20efficient%20cooking%20solution%20and%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20'chulhas'.%20It%20cuts%20smoke%2C%20saves%20fuel%2C%20and%20helps%20rural%20women%20save%20time%20and%20effort%20while%20reducing%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342452%2Ftraditional-chulha-smoke-while-cooking-greenway-grameen-ankit-mathur-neha-juneja-smart-stove%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20If%20Each%20Indian%20Could%20Sponsor%20Nutrition%20For%201%20Malnourished%20Child%3F%20IAS%20Officer%20Makes%20it%20Possible%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20September%2C%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20Pooja%20Bai%20Kol%E2%80%99s%20toddler%20Deepanshu%20fell%20sick.%20For%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20her%20son%20suffered%20severe%20diarrhoea%2C%20making%20him%20so%20weak%20that%20the%20family%20had%20to%20admit%20him%20to%20the%20nearby%20nutrition%20rehabilitation%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20to%20a%20family%20of%20daily%20wagers%2C%20the%20child%20was%20malnourished.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20weighed%20nine%20kg%20then%2C%20whereas%2C%20he%20should%20ideally%20have%20been%20above%2010%20kg.%20We%20lacked%20enough%20resources%20to%20offer%20him%20good%20nutritional%20food.%20I%20cooked%20lentils%20only%20on%20alternate%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pooja%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20treatment%20that%20continued%20for%20seven%20days%2C%20Pooja%20brought%20her%20son%20back%20home.%20Deeply%20concerned%20for%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20heave%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief%20only%20after%20three%20months%20when%20Deepanshu%20finally%20showed%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20including%20green%20vegetables%20like%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20all%20kinds%20of%20lentils%2C%20soybean%20%3Cem%3Ebari%20%3C%2Fem%3E(nuggets)%2C%20jaggery%2C%20peanuts%2C%20%3Cem%3Esattu%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20milk%2C%20and%20grams%20in%20his%20diet.%20My%20son%20now%20weighs%2010.5%20kg.%20He%20remains%20happy%20and%20plays%20all%20day%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%2027-year-old%20resident%20of%20Dhanvahi%20village%20in%20Katni%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-3-1708432539.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deepanshu%20before%20and%20after%20receiving%20the%20treatment%20and%20nutritional%20care.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-3-1708432539.jpg%201200w