cle%20in%20the%20Hindustan%20newspaper%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20special%20supplement%20to%20mark%20the%20ceremonies%20which%20took%C2%A0place%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20at%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20Keerthik%20Sasidharan%20who%20made%20the%20Hindi%20text%20available%20to%20me%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20translate%20it.%20I%E2%80%99m%20grateful%20to%20Philip%20Lutgendorf%20and%20Akhilesh%20Mani%20Shandilya%20with%20whom%20I%2C%20along%20with%20my%20colleagues%2C%20was%20able%20to%20discuss%20Tulsidas%20in%20the%20winter%20of%202023-24%2C%20and%20to%20Linda%20Hess%20and%20Purushottam%20Agrawal%20from%20whom%20I%20keep%20on%20learning%20about%20Kabir).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKailash%C2%A0Vajpeyi%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20(1936-2015)%20was%20a%20poet%2C%20scholar%2C%20broadcaster%20and%20public%20intellectual%20who%20wrote%20extensively%20in%20Hindi%20and%20English.%20He%20received%20many%20literary%20awards%20and%20his%20work%20is%20translated%20into%20many%20languages.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fananya-vajpeyi%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAnanya%C2%A0Vajpeyi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20writer%20and%20scholar%20based%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708364185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20220247%2FKings-Valley.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fkailash-vajpeyi-ram-in-our-faith%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20figure%20of%20Ram%20has%20been%20reinscribed%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20a%20form%20that%20goes%20against%20everything%20we%20have%20known%20and%20loved%20about%20him%20for%20centuries.%20A%20reminder%20of%20the%20true%20Ram%20we%20are%20in%20danger%C2%A0of%20forgetting%20seemed%20in%20order.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22htt