0their%20first%20order.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaroj%20would%20make%20and%20pack%20the%20pickle%20and%20Amit%20helped%20her%20brand%2C%20label%20and%20dispatch%20it.%20In%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20their%20business%20grew%20and%20they%20had%20to%20set%20up%20a%20bigger%20space%20and%20hire%20women.%20Today%2C%20the%2043-year-old%20sells%20over%20800%20pickles%20per%20month%20and%20earns%20Rs%202.5%20lakhs%20per%20month%20seven%20months%20after%20starting%20her%20business.%20The%20woman%20who%20never%20set%20foot%20in%20a%20school%20is%20providing%20employment%20to%2030%20women%20today%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20did%20she%20set%20up%20a%20business%20from%20scratch%20with%20no%20prior%20experience%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20her%20incredible%20story%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20made%20my%20first%20pickle%20at%2015%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20853px)%20100vw%2C%20853px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSaroj5-1708349551.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saroj%20started%20her%20pickle%20business%20in%20June%202023%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSaroj5-1708349551.jpeg%20853w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSaroj5-1708349551-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSaroj5-1708349551-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSaroj5-1708349551-768x1152.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSaroj5-1708349551-150x225.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342276%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaroj%20started%20her%20pickle%20business%20in%20June%202023%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Berkhedi%20village%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Saroj%20was%20one%20among%20nine%20daughters.%20Her%20parents%20were%20farmers%20and%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20many%20education%20opportunities%20for%20them.%20She%20spent%20her%20childhood%20on%20the%20fields%20watching%20her%20mother%20make%20food%20and%20pickles%2C%20eventually%20picking%20up%20the%20skills%20from%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20learnt%20to%20cook%20everything%2C%20what%20really%20fascinated%20her%20were%20pickles.%20She%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20she%20made%20a%20raw%20mango%20pickle%20for%20the%20first%20time%20as%20a%2015-year-old.%20Little%20did%20she%20know%20that%20this%20would%20help%20her%20live%20her%20entrepreneurship%20dream%20almost%2018%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20was%20the%20norm%20then%2C%20she%20was%20married%20at%2020%20and%20moved%20to%20Shadora.%20Soon%2C%20she%20was%20busy%20with%20responsibilities%20at%20home%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20two%20children.%20But%20her%20husband%2C%20Bablu%20Prajapati%2C%20always%20encouraged%20her%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20I%20had%20seen%20before%20marriage%20was%20our%20village.%20My%20husband%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339969%2Fadil-qadri-attar-perfumes-shark-tank-india-entrepreneur-asthma-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewanted%20me%20to%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20participate%20in%20matters%20of%20local%20governance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saroj%20shares%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20opportunity%20presented%20itself%20to%20contribute%20to%20her%20community%2C%20she%20grabbed%20it%2C%20and%C2%A0%20served%20as%20the%20village%20sarpanch%20for%20eight%20years.%20During%20her%20tenure%2C%20she%20met%20many%20women%20from%20rural