oads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-11-1708004888-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341973%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20has%20helped%20175%20students%20get%20their%20dream%20university.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbitio%20began%20with%20a%20core%20challenge%20we%20aimed%20to%20address%3A%20simplifying%20the%20admissions%20process%20for%20students%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20developed%20a%20platform%20product%20designed%20to%20support%20students%20throughout%20their%20entire%20admissions%20journey.%20Our%20ultimate%20objective%20is%20to%20establish%20a%20comprehensive%20global%20AI%20admissions%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CRegardless%20of%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20background%20or%20location%2C%20our%20aim%20is%20to%20provide%20equal%20opportunities%20and%20access%20to%20the%20right%20guidance%2C%20a%20privilege%20often%20reserved%20for%20the%20affluent%20or%20those%20able%20to%20afford%20expensive%20counsellors.%20We%20leverage%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F126973%2Fkerala-police-equips-personnel-cutting-edge-body-cameras%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting-edge%20technology%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20AI%2C%20to%20achieve%20this%20goal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20AI%20comes%20into%20play%20with%20the%20process%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20employ%20AI%20in%20two%20primary%20areas.%20Firstly%2C%20we%20utilise%20it%20to%20assist%20students%20in%20determining%20the%20most%20suitable%20program%20or%20university%20currently%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20While%20there%20are%20existing%20filtration%20tools%20enabling%20students%20to%20filter%20courses%20they%20are%20eligible%20for%20and%20view%20them%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20an%20additional%20step%20forward.%20We%20incorporate%20preferences%20into%20the%20equation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20AI%20strives%20to%20understand%20and%20integrate%20the%20individual%20preferences%20of%20each%20student%20into%20the%20recommendations%20that%20it%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20accomplish%20this%20through%20our%20proprietary%20recommendation%20engine%2C%20which%20has%20been%20trained%20on%20over%2015%20million%20acceptance%20and%20admit%20data%20points.%20While%20it%E2%80%99s%20certainly%20possible%20for%20students%20to%20conduct%20this%20research%20themselves%20by%20visiting%20numerous%20websites%2C%20reading%20various%20articles%2C%20and%20compiling%20the%20information%20manually%2C%20our%20platform%20streamlines%20this%20process%20significantly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20synthesising%20and%20analysing%20vast%20amounts%20of%20information%2C%20the%20platform%20can%20deliver%20personalised%20recommendations%20quickly%20and%20seamlessly%2C%20saving%20students%20valuable%20time%20and%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20where%20AI%20comes%20in%20to%20help%20the%20students%20is%20writing%20their%20personal%20essays.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20students%20know%20what%20college%20they%20want%2C%20the%20next%20step%20is%20to%20write%20a%20stellar%20essay.%20We%20trained%20our%20model%20with%205%2C000%20accepted%20essays%20from%20across%20universities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20begin%20by%20ensuring%20basic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341068%2Fteach-spoken-english-on-youtube-dehati-madam-uttar-pradesh-yashoda-lodhi-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrammar%20and%20punctuation%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20correct.%20Beyond%20these%20fundamentals%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20delivery%20and%20specificity.%20Delivery%20pertains%20to%20how%20effectively%20the%20essay%20is%20conveyed%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20while%20specificity%20refers%20to%20its%20relevance%20to%20the%20programme%20being%20applied%20for%20and%20the%20individual%20applicant%E2%80%99s%20profile.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqYHd6FBTi0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqYHd6FBTi0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqYHd6FBTi0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Ambitio%20(%40ambitio.club)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20it%20as%20a%20personalised%20Grammarly%20tool%20tailored%20specifically%20for%20college%20applications!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20platform%20is%20mostly%20free%20for%20students%20except%20for%20the%20phase%20where%20they%20need%20effective%20management%20of%20their%20essays%20and%20applications.%20This%20phase%20comes%20under%20a%20small%20paid%20subscription.%20Before%20this%20phase%2C%20everything%20else%20from%20finding%20the%20right%20college%20to%20applying%20for%20a%20scholarship%20comes%20under%20the%20free%20subscription%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20also%20recently%20raised%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20in%20a%20pre-seed%20round%20of%20funding%20from%20First%20Cheque%20and%20angel%20investors%20from%20the%20US%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20future%20plans%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20entail%20aggressive%20growth%20within%20the%20Indian%20market.%20Presently%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20managing%20around%20200%20students%20in%20this%20intake%2C%20and%20we%20aim%20to%20scale%20up%20to%202%2C500%20within%20the%20upcoming%20financial%20year.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20are%20planning%20to%20expand%20our%20services%20to%20include%20undergraduate%20admissions%20as%20well.%20This%20strategic%20expansion%20will%20allow%20us%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20broader%20range%20of%20students%20and%20further%20establish%20ourselves%20as%20a%20comprehensive%20admissions%20platform.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Ambitio)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708062714000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341947%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IIT%20graduates%20Dirghayu%20Kaushik%2C%20Vikrant%20Shivalik%20and%20Vaibhav%20Tyagi%20started%20Ambitio%20to%20help%20Indian%20students%20get%20into%20their%20dream%20universities%20abroad.%20The%20AI-powered%20free%20platform%20helps%20students%20find%20the%20right%20colleges%20and%20even%20in%20filling%20applications%20and%20writing%20personal%20essays.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341947%2Funiversity-admission-counselling-abroad-ambitio-startup-ai-dream-college-uk-us-canada-iit%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Startup%20Is%20Building%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98First%20Green%20Hydrogen%20Plant%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20hydrogen%20is%20being%20heavily%20used%20in%20powering%20vehicles%2C%20oil%20refining%2C%20ammonia%20production%2C%20steel%20production%2C%20and%20to%20generate%20electricity.%20All%20of%20this%20hydrogen%20is%20supplied%20using%20fossil%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Freports%2Fthe-future-of-hydrogen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Energy%20Agency%20%3C%2Fa%3E(IEA)%2C%20the%20production%20of%20hydrogen%20is%20responsible%20for%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%20of%20around%20830%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20per%20year.%20Interestingly%2C%20green%20hydrogen%20%E2%80%93%20produced%20by%20the%20electrolysis%20of%20water%20using%20renewable%20electricity%20%E2%80%93%20could%20save%20tonnes%20of%20this%20carbon%20dioxide%20emitted%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tap%20into%20green%20hydrogen%E2%80%99s%20potential%20and%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20a%20clean%2C%20secure%2C%20and%20affordable%20energy%20future%2C%20Haryana-based%20green%20hydrogen%20company%2C%20Hygenco%2C%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20construct%20and%20operate%20a%20100%20percent%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20would%20be%20the%20first%20operative%20green%20hydrogen%20production%20facility%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20will%20produce%20energy%20without%20emitting%20carbon%20dioxide%20into%20the%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Amit%20Bansal%2C%20CEO%20of%20Hygenco%20Green%20Energies%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20rapid%20pace%20of%20growth%20is%20already%20entailing%20a%20significant%20surge%20in%20the%20use%20of%20resources%2C%20especially%